I am married and have two children. I like spending time with my family, attending and supporting my children with their sporting events and school activities. In my spare time, I enjoy reading, journaling, and walking. I am very interested in the nursing field, and feel I have learned a lot working daily along side a Nurse Practitioner. I want to continue to obtain more knowledge about the health care field, and desire to be an asset to any health care team.
